133
00:07:47,025 --> 00:07:48,906
So we picked a state with just one tree,

134
00:07:48,926 --> 00:07:53,209
so there could be a standoff as players try to avoid doing the second last hit.

135
00:07:55,030 --> 00:07:58,513
And sometimes you need to invent entirely new rules, like in Rampage,

136
00:07:58,653 --> 00:08:00,895
where we challenge players to avoid touching the ground.

