1303
01:27:12,576 --> 01:27:14,896
that didn't just have a story about a long-distance relationship,

1304
01:27:15,316 --> 01:27:19,417
but mechanics to help enhance that feeling of being apart from someone that you loved.

1305
01:27:20,525 --> 01:27:22,006
And we didn't really know how to do that at first.

1306
01:27:22,507 --> 01:27:24,569
