1325
01:28:15,578 --> 01:28:18,119
So that provides the basis for our game of Fold Apart.

1326
01:28:18,779 --> 01:28:21,240
It's a puzzle game about a long distance relationship

1327
01:28:23,040 --> 01:28:24,221
in a world made out of paper.

1328
01:28:26,261 --> 01:28:28,562
